litet. Blodet burde ha blitt testet, men Helge fikk ikke engang mulighet til det. Blodet blir uansett sikret f\u00f8r det blir gitt videre, p\u00e5peker hun."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "eec2eacb53d4f7425050a6f3e0bd6ac795c716d681865bb1c2beebb98a9d0ef3"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2017-04-30T10:24:23.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Helge Hestnes ble avvist da han kom for \u00e5 gi blod. Begrunnelsen var at han er gift med en brasiliansk kvinne."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article1135631.ece5/ALTERNATES/w980-default/blod8"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/498d9821e6ae78b1cab5425ed49add7819140749.jpg?598a8b08"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["Kona er fra Brasil - f\u00e5r ikke gi blod -adressa.no", "Frustrert", "F\u00f8ler seg diskriminert"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "498d9821e6ae78b1cab5425ed49add7819140749"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["utenriks", "innenriks", "trondheim", "E6", "midtbyen", "bybrann", "bilulykker"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "utenriks,innenriks,trondheim,E6,midtbyen,bybrann,bilulykker"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "law-government-and-politics"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["blodgiver", "diskriminert", "blod"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["r\u00f8de kors", "nardo", "adresseavisen"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": ["norge", "brasil", "frankrike"]}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "value": ["andr\u00e9a carneiro hestnes", "helge hestnes", "bengt eidems"]}, {"field": "kw-taxonomy", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "og-image", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article1135631.ece5/ALTERNATES/w980-default/blod8"}, {"field": "